The keyframes have been successfully extracted from the video. Now I need to convert each frame to grayscale using the image editing skill.

```json
{
  "analysis": "Keyframes have been extracted to /root/keyframes_001.png, /root/keyframes_002.png, etc. Now I need to convert each frame to grayscale. I'll use the image editing skill to convert the RGB images to grayscale in-place.",
  "plan": "Use the image editing skill to convert each keyframe from RGB to grayscale. The command will process each file in the /root directory that matches the keyframe pattern.",
  "commands": [
    {
      "keystrokes": "mogrify -path /root -format png -colorspace gray /root/keyframes_*.png\n",
      "duration": 1.0
    }
  ]
}
```
